ric series) and <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_983\"><?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?> <math alttext=\"a_{i}=1/i^{2}\" display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msub> <mi>a</mi> <mi>i</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <mn>1</mn> <mo>/</mo> <msup> <mi>i</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> </mrow> </math></span> and it seems to always diverge.</p>",
